### Phase 8 UAT: AI Chat Endpoint (Type-Safe Routes)
### Server must be running on localhost:8080

### Step 1: Login to get access token
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "ignis.fatue@gmail.com",
  "password": "Mm.12345"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("accessToken", response.body.accessToken);
%}

### Step 2: POST /api/ai/chat (type-safe route)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/ai/chat
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "message": "Hello, what can you help me with?"
}

### Step 3: POST /api/ai/assistant (type-safe route)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/ai/assistant
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "message": "How many users are registered?"
}
